'''Izem''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: ''Panthera leo'') s d [[aɣersiw]] [[timseksumin|amseksum]] n [[tawacult (tasnudert)|twacult]] n [[tiserɣuda|tserɣuda]] yeṭṭafaren [[Tawsit (tudersent)|Tawsit]] n [[aɣilas (tawsit)|iɣilasen]], 
Izmawen ttidiren ass-a deg [[Tafriqt|Tefriqt n unẓul n taneẓruft]] akken i mazal degsen taɣreft meẓẓiyen deg  [Asya]] tettwaggez s [[angar|umihi n ungar]], ziktallit n [[azarmezruy|uzarmezruy]] llan ttidiren ula deg [[Turuft]], aɣeṛsiw-agi yenger deg tmiḍi tis snat [[send n tlallit]] imi aṭas i yettazzalen deffir-s akken ad t-gemren. 
 
Zik nni, Izem deg [[Tafriqt|Tefriqt]] yella yettidir deg yal tama, deg yal tamurt ula di [[taneẓruft|tneẓruft]] yakk d idurar am [[Idurar n Aṭlas|idurar n waṭlas]]. Maca ass-a grant-d kra kan n tɣerfin yessufin (yettwaɛezlen) aladɣa deg tmura n usamar n Tefrikt

 ɣas ma yella izmawen ttbanen-aɣ-d meṛṛa kifkif-iten deg ṣṣifa, maca sɛan aṭas n tdulemsin (sous-espèces) yettemgaraden ciṭ deg ṣṣifa akk d tiddi. Ger tlemsin (leṣnaf) n yizmawen yettidiren deg Tefriqt, nezmer ad d-nebder izem n [[Tamazɣa|Tmazɣa]] (lion de Barbarie, Panthera leo leo). D netta i d izem ameqqran akk yettwassnen, yernu ass-a yenger. Izem n Yimassayen (Panthera leo massaicus, semman-as ɣef yisem n yiwen wegdud n Tefriqt, Imassayen ikessen izgaren), d izem-nni ay yettidiren deg tsabant (savane) n [[Kenya]] d [[Tanzanya]], deg [[Tafriqt tacerqit|Tefriqt tacerqit]]. Izem-agi meqqer ciṭṭ, yettidir deg uzaɣar anda ay yettṣeggid izgaren d yiɣersiwen niḍen. 
 
Deg [[Asya]], mazal izem la yettidir deg tmurt n [[Lhend]], deg yiwet n tama qqaren-as Gir. Ṣṣenf-agi qqaren-as "izem n Asya" (Panthera leo persica) u qqimen-d kan seg-s 200. ɣas ma yella deg kra n tmura izem ur yettwassen ara neɣ ur t-mazal ara la yettidir dinna, maca medden ssnen-t, yesɛa isem deg tutlayin-nsen yernu yella deg tmucuha-nsen d tẓuryin-nsen. 
 
Deg Tuṛuft, izem yenger azal n 20 tasutin ay-a, maca deg tasut-agi meṛṛa, medden akk la ttmeslayen fell-as, u mazal aɣersiw-agi yella deg tsugint-nsen. 
 
Deg tmurt-nneɣ, izem mazal yettwassen yisem-is yernu yettwabdar-d ama deg yinzan neɣ deg tmucuha, u d aɣersiw yesɛan azal meqqren ɣer-neɣ imi izem d azamul n tezmert akk d tebɣest (lkuṛaj). 
 
Deg Ccinwa, ɣas ma yella nnan-d werǧin yedder yizem dinna, maca ar ass-a nezmer ad nwali isebdaden n yizmawen deg leqṣur i bnan Yicinwaten n zik. ɣer Yicinwaten, izem yessebɛad yir leṛwaḥ, daɣen sseqdacen asebded-yines akken "ad iḥudd" leqṣur-nsen. Nnig n waya, Icinwaten sɛan awitay i deg ḥessben agguren-nsen d yiseggasen-nsen i yiman-nsen, dɣa yal asseggwas ttaken-as Yicinwaten isem, akken daɣen i yella ɣer-sen "useggas n yizem". 
 
Izem n Tmazɣa yenger aṭas ay-a seg tmura-nneɣ. Izem aneggaru akk ay yettwanɣan deg [[Dzayer|Lezzayer]], nɣan-t deg tgara n tasut wis 19 deg tama n Souk Ahras, deg ccerq n tmurt. Ma izem aneggaru akk n [[Meṛṛuk]], nɣan-t deg 1922. D acu kan, gwran-d kra seg yizmawen n Tmazɣa deg yelmaten n yiɣersiwen (zoos) deg kra n temdinin deg ddunit, am deg Rbaṭ, tamaneɣt n Meṛṛuk. Kra n yemnuda n tesdawit n Oxford, nudan ad d-rren izem n Tmazɣa ɣer yiwen wefrag aɣelnaw (parc national) deg yidurar n Waṭlas ameṛṛuki, maca ɣef wakken ɣriɣ, asenfar-agi (projet) yeḥbes imi tarbaɛt i d-yelhan yid-s xuṣṣen-tt yedrimen.

